lead_paragraph: Minnesota's 10-game homestand started fast with a leadoff inside-the-park home run by Eduardo Nunez. Buoyed by a season-high 15 hits for the Twins, the bullpen finished strong.

headline.print_headline: Twins Bullpen Locks Up 6-4 Win Over Reeling Rays
